### Hadith 1:120

*Narrated Ibrahim bin Al-Mundhir:*

Ibn Abi Fudaik narrated the same as above (Hadith...119) but added that
the Prophet had moved his hands as if filling them with something and
then he emptied them in the Rida' of Abu Huraira.

